==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: go-getter
<hw>go-getter</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person disposed to initiate
action, rather than take instructions; an enterprising person; a person
with a strong drive to accomplish useful goals; especially, one whose
career progresses rapidly.</def> <wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> whizz-kid, whiz-kid, ball of fire.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

